name: IEEE 2023 The 5th International Conference on System Reliability and Safety Engineering (IEEE SRSE 2023)
content: Conference Proceedings: Accepted and presented papers will be published by \*SRSE IEEE conference proceedings\*. Published papers are expected to be included in \*IEEE Xplore\*, and indexed by\* EI Compendex, Scopus\* and other academical databases etc. Special Issue on Quality and Reliability Engineering International (QREI), IF: 3; Index: SCIE, EI Compendex, SCOPUS, etc.
